message.body: Hey sofie I just got out of my interview. I think it went really well! Are you available or giving tours?
Oh I'm running up to ninth flr to wait for a tour! You still here?

Shoot just left, I gotta catch the train back to providence. No worries though let's talk soon. Lemme know if you hear anything else from jan or brian. I might come up again soon for a full tour. When do you usually give them?
